Furthermore, the paper's focus on understanding how deep neural networks work and their decision-making behavior suggests that it could also belong to the sub-category of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). 

The paper's use of deep neural network models also suggests that it could belong to the sub-category of cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
